description: Disallow code comments in this project
alwaysApply: true
---

# No Comments in Code

- The AI assistant must **not add comments** to any code it writes or edits.
- When modifying existing code, **do not introduce new comments**, even if surrounding code already has comments.
- Prefer clear, self-explanatory names and structure instead of comments for explaining intent.
- If an explanation is necessary, provide it **only in the chat response**, not in the code.
